<div class="policy-content">

  <h5>1. Introduction</h5>
  <p>
    Welcome to Shony Talks. These Terms & Conditions govern your access to and use of our platform, including all courses, plans, and digital services. By using our website, you agree to be bound by these terms. If you do not agree, please refrain from using our services.
  </p>

  <h5>2. Eligibility</h5>
  <p>
    To use our platform, you must be at least 18 years old or accessing the platform under the supervision of a parent or guardian. You agree to provide accurate, complete, and current information during registration and to keep it updated at all times.
  </p>

  <h5>3. Services</h5>
  <p>
    Shony Talks provides online learning resources, including individual courses and bundled plans. Access duration may vary depending on the product purchased, and details will be clearly mentioned at the time of purchase.
  </p>

  <h5>4. User Responsibilities</h5>
  <p>
    You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account credentials. Any activity performed through your account is considered your responsibility. Misuse of the platform, including sharing login credentials or attempting unauthorized access, is strictly prohibited.
  </p>

  <h5>5. Payments</h5>
  <p>
    All payments are processed securely through trusted third-party payment providers. We do not store your payment details. Access to purchased content will be granted only after successful payment confirmation.
  </p>

  <h5>6. Refund Policy</h5>
  <p>
    All purchases are final and non-refundable unless otherwise stated. Refunds may be considered only in exceptional cases such as duplicate transactions or technical errors, subject to verification.
  </p>

  <h5>7. Intellectual Property</h5>
  <p>
    All content available on Shony Talks, including videos, text, graphics, and course materials, is the intellectual property of the platform. You may not reproduce, distribute, or share any content without prior written permission.
  </p>

  <h5>8. Account Suspension</h5>
  <p>
    We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account without prior notice if we detect any violation of these terms or suspicious activity that may harm the platform or other users.
  </p>

  <h5>9. Limitation of Liability</h5>
  <p>
    Shony Talks shall not be held liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use or inability to use our services. We do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free access at all times.
  </p>

  <h5>10. Changes to Terms</h5>
  <p>
    We may update these Terms & Conditions from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and continued use of the platform after such updates constitutes your acceptance of the revised terms.
  </p>

  <h5>11. Contact Information</h5>
  <p>
    If you have any questions or concerns regarding these terms, please contact us at 
    <b>shonytalks@gmail.com</b>.
  </p>

